query:
INSERT INTO auth_refresh_tokens (
                token_hash,
                user_id,
                device_session_id,
                session_id,
                device_name,
                expires_at,
                metadata
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, NULL, NULL, $3, $4, $5)
            ON CONFLICT (token_hash) DO UPDATE
            SET revoked = false,
                revoked_at = NULL,
                revoked_reason = NULL,
                expires_at = EXCLUDED.expires_at,
                device_name = EXCLUDED.device_name,
                metadata = EXCLUDED.metadata
